name: Gustavus Adolphus College
Wamo_LA: 58  In 2017, Gustavus was ranked 77th in the national liberal arts college category and 45th in the Best Value Schools category by ''U.S. News & World Report''.  ''The Wall Street Journal''/''Times Higher Education'' college rankings placed Gustavus 48th on its list of the top 100 liberal arts colleges in the United States in 2017, |
